<D>__{you were kind of a double kid, i bet, right? one kid with your old man. one kid with your mother. upper middle class in the week, and then dropping your 'r's and hanging in the southie projects with daddy the donkey on the weekends. i got that right?}
<A>__{billy, opened up expertly and crudely, stares with contained hatred.}
